/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGYR$SET_DATE_FORMAT */
BEGIN
  set_application_property(DATE_FORMAT_COMPATIBILITY_MODE, '5.0');
  set_application_property(PLSQL_DATE_FORMAT, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS');
  set_application_property(BUILTIN_DATE_FORMAT, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS');
  forms_ddl('ALTER SESSION SET NLS_DATE_FORMAT = ''YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS''');
END;

/* CGNV$PRE_FORM_NAVCUR */
  DECLARE
  rg_id RECORDGROUP;
  gc_wnd GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_item GROUPCOLUMN;
BEGIN
  CGNV$.nav_opening_wnd := FALSE;
  rg_id := create_group('CGNV$WINDOW_ITEM');
  gc_wnd := add_group_column(rg_id, 'WINDOW', CHAR_COLUMN, 80);
  gc_item := add_group_column(rg_id, 'ITEM', CHAR_COLUMN, 80);
  add_group_row(rg_id, 1);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 1, 'CALENDAR');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 1, 'CALENDAR.OK');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 2);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 2, 'COMPROBANTES');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 2, 'CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 3);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 3, 'CNTPGRCNTW');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 3, 'OBLCNT.REG_ACTUAL');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 4);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_wnd, 4, 'WINDOW');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_item, 4, 'CGNV$WINDOW_1.BOT_PLAN_DE_CUENTAS');
END;

/* CGNV$PRE_FORM_NAVCCF */
  DECLARE
  rg_id RECORDGROUP;
  gc_type GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_name GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_parent GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_tag GROUPCOLUMN;
  gc_extra GROUPCOLUMN;
BEGIN
  CGNV$.nav_close_forms := TRUE;
  CGNV$.nav_opening_wnd := FALSE;
  rg_id := create_group('CGSH$FORM_OBJECTS');
  gc_type := add_group_column(rg_id, 'OBJECT_TYPE', CHAR_COLUMN, 2);
  gc_name := add_group_column(rg_id, 'OBJECT_NAME', CHAR_COLUMN, 40);
  gc_parent := add_group_column(rg_id, 'PARENT_NAME', CHAR_COLUMN, 40);
  gc_tag := add_group_column(rg_id, 'ITEM_TAG', CHAR_COLUMN, 40);
  gc_extra := add_group_column(rg_id, 'EXTRA_TEXT', CHAR_COLUMN, 240);
  add_group_row(rg_id, 1);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 1, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 1, 'CALENDAR');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 1, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 2);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 2, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 2, 'COMPROBANTES');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 2, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 3);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 3, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 3, 'CNTPGRCNTW');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 3, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 4);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 4, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 4, 'WINDOW');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 4, '');
  add_group_row(rg_id, 5);
  set_group_char_cell(gc_type, 5, 'WN');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_name, 5, 'QMS$HIDDEN_ITEMS');
  set_group_char_cell(gc_parent, 5, '');
END;

/* CGLT$TAB_BLOCK_MANAGEMENT                */
/* Switch tab management code on/off        */
DECLARE
   current_canvas VARCHAR2(61) := GET_ITEM_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.CURSOR_ITEM, ITEM_CANVAS);
   base_canvas VARCHAR2(61);
BEGIN
   CGLY$GET_RELATED_CANVASES(current_canvas, base_canvas);
   IF( base_canvas IN ( 'CG$PAGE_1' ) ) THEN
      CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.ACTIVATE := TRUE;
   ELSE
      CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.ACTIVATE := FALSE;
   END IF;
END;
/* CGLY$MANAGE_CANVASES */
BEGIN
  CGLY$CANVAS_MANAGEMENT;
END;


/* CGLT$TAB_NEW_BLOCK                      */
/* Show canvases for this block            */
BEGIN
   IF CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.ACTIVATE = TRUE THEN
      CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.CGLT$NEW_BLOCK;
   END IF;
END;

/* CGBS$WHEN_NEW_BLOCK_INSTANCE */
BEGIN
  CGBS$.NEW_BLOCK( :SYSTEM.CURSOR_BLOCK, :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE);
END;

/*
 CREADO POR: Juan Carlos Cabrera
 PROPOSITO:  Maximizar la ventana principal y descapacitar el boton de impresión si no tiene
             un reporte asociado
 FECHA:      26/NOV/1999
*/
  SET_WINDOW_PROPERTY(FORMS_MDI_WINDOW,WINDOW_STATE,MAXIMIZE);
  IF :GLOBAL.CG$REPORTE IS NULL THEN
    QMS$TOOLBAR.HIDE_BUTTON('PRINT');
  END IF;
end;
/* CGGN$CALL_GENERATOR_CODE */

  CGBS2$.SET_COORD_STYLE( 'W' );
  CGBS2$.SET_QRY_ON_ENTRY( 'Y' );
  BEGIN
    CG$WHEN_NEW_FORM_INSTANCE;
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
END;

BEGIN
  set_window_property ('COMPROBANTES',WINDOW_STATE,MAXIMIZE);
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.ASOCIACION',VISIBLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.BTNOBL',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('vEmp_Cod',:GLOBAL.CG$EMPRESA_CODIGO);
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('vTpo_Cmp','');
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('dFecha','');
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('nClave','');
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('vImprimir','');
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('vMoneda','');
  AÑADIR_PARAMETROS('vMonedaLocal','');
  DEFAULT_VALUE('','GLOBAL.TITULO_OBLIGACIONES'); -- Guarda el titulo de la ventana de obligaciones
END;

BEGIN
-- Redefinimos la secuenca de movimientos del comprobante
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.CUENTA2',NEXT_NAVIGATION_ITEM,'MVM.DESCRIPCION');
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.DESCRIPCION',PREVIOUS_NAVIGATION_ITEM,'MVM.CUENTA2');
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.ASOCIACION',NEXT_NAVIGATION_ITEM,'MVM.DEBEM');
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.DEBEM',PREVIOUS_NAVIGATION_ITEM,'MVM.ASOCIACION');
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.HABERM',NEXT_NAVIGATION_ITEM,'MVM.CAMPO_TEMPORAL');
END;

/* CGNV$WHEN_WINDOW_ACTIVATED */
BEGIN
  IF( (:SYSTEM.CURSOR_ITEM IS NOT NULL) AND
      (:SYSTEM.EVENT_WINDOW) !=
       CGNV$GET_ITEM_WINDOW(:SYSTEM.CURSOR_ITEM) ) THEN
    CGNV$.NAVIGATE_TO_WINDOW(:SYSTEM.EVENT_WINDOW);
  END IF;
END;

/* CGBS$ON_CLEAR_DETAILS */
BEGIN
  IF (FORM_FAILURE and :SYSTEM.COORDINATION_OPERATION in ('MOUSE', 'DUPLICATE_RECORD')) THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (:SYSTEM.MASTER_BLOCK = :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK) THEN
    CGBS$.CLEAR_MASTER_DETAIL( :SYSTEM.MASTER_BLOCK, :SYSTEM.COORDINATION_OPERATION );
  END IF;
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        No
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------
   * Name                                            ON-POPULATE-DETAILS
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   - Trigger Style                                   PL/SQL
   * Trigger Text                                    

/* CGBS$ON_POPULATE_DETAILS */
BEGIN
  CGBS$.QUERY_DETAILS( :SYSTEM.CURSOR_BLOCK, :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE );
END;

   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes

/* CGBS$KEY_ENTQRY_FRM */
BEGIN
  IF (get_block_property( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, QUERY_ALLOWED) = 'FALSE') THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(37, 'Consulta no permitida en este bloque'), 'E', 'OFG', 37);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END IF;
  CGBS$.DO_KEYQRY( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, 'ENTER_QUERY', :SYSTEM.MODE);
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        Yes
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------

  END IF;

/* CGBS$KEY_CLRBLK_FRM */
BEGIN
  IF ( CGBS2$.IS_RECORD_DIRTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK) ) THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (:SYSTEM.BLOCK_STATUS = 'CHANGED' or CGBS2$.IS_COMMIT_NEEDED( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK ) ) THEN
    CGBS2$.DO_COMMIT_DIALOGUE;
  END IF;
  clear_block( NO_VALIDATE );
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        Yes
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------
   * Name                                            KEY-CLRREC
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   - Trigger Style                                   PL/SQL
   * Trigger Text                                    

/* CGBS$KEY_CLRREC */
BEGIN
  IF ( CGBS2$.IS_RECORD_DIRTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK) ) THEN
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (:SYSTEM.BLOCK_STATUS = 'CHANGED' or CGBS2$.IS_COMMIT_NEEDED( :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK ) ) THEN
    CGBS2$.DO_COMMIT_DIALOGUE;
  END IF;
  clear_record;
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        Yes
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------
   * Name                                            KEY-NXTKEY
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   - Trigger Style                                   PL/SQL
   * Trigger Text

  qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(30, 'Clave no válida en este contexto'), 'E', 'OFG', 30);
  qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        No

/* CGLT$NEW_TAB_PAGE                  */
/* Show related canvases for this tab */
BEGIN
   IF( :SYSTEM.TAB_NEW_PAGE IN ( 'CG$M_TAB_1_PAGE_1', 'CG$M_TAB_1_PAGE_2' ) ) THEN
      CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.ACTIVATE := TRUE;
      CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.CGLT$TAB_CHANGED;
   END IF;
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        No
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------
   * Name                                            KEY-COMMIT
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   - Trigger Style                                   PL/SQL
   * Trigger Text                                    

BEGIN
QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_DEBUG_INFO('KEY-COMMIT');
  VALIDATE(RECORD_SCOPE);
  REFLEJAR_DATOS_PARA_RTN; -- nos aseguramos que los movimientos reflejen las asociaciones
  IF NOT FORM_SUCCESS THEN
    RETURN; -- si falla algo al validar no grabamos nada
  END IF;
  COMMIT_FORM;
  IF :SYSTEM.FORM_STATUS='QUERY' AND :CMP.RETENCIONES='V' AND :PARAMETER.GRABADO='V' THEN
    RECONSULTAR_HIJOS;
  END IF;
EXCEPTION
  WHEN OTHERS THEN
    QMS$ERRORS.UNHANDLED_EXCEPTION('KEY-COMMIT');
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        No
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------
   * Name                                            POST-DATABASE-COMMIT
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   - Trigger Style                                   PL/SQL
   * Trigger Text                                    

BEGIN
  Fijar_Parametros_Reportes;
END;

DECLARE
  nRecCmp NUMBER:=TO_NUMBER(GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('CMP',CURRENT_RECORD));
  nCmpFechaItm ITEM:=FIND_ITEM('CMP.FECHA');
  nMvmBlq BLOCK:=FIND_BLOCK('MVM');
  nAscCmpBlq BLOCK:=FIND_BLOCK('ASCCMP');
BEGIN
  IF :CMP.ESTADO='N' THEN
-- Una vez grabado los cambios habilitamos la actualizacion de
-- fechas de comprobantes solo si el estado del comprobante no es cerrado ni anulado
    SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY(nCmpFechaItm,nRecCmp,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,DELETE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
--  SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  END IF;
END;
   * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                        No
   - Execution Hierarchy                             Override
   * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                      Yes
   - 'Keyboard Help' Text                            
   - Trigger Steps                                   
   ----------
   * Name                                            PRE-COMMIT
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   - Trigger Style                                   PL/SQL
   * Trigger Text                                    

BEGIN
  Crear_Grupo_Comprobantes;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_LOOKUP_DATA */
BEGIN
    IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        CGFK$QRY_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK(:CMP.NOMBRE_REPORTE ,:CMP.OBLIGACIONES ,:CMP.RETENCIONES ,:CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA ,:CMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD ,:CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE ,:CMP.NOMBRE ,:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO);
      EXCEPTION
        WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('Tipo de Comprobante no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        WHEN OTHERS THEN
          CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
      END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'CMP', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
    ELSE
        qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(78, 'Debe especificar <p1>', 'Comprobante' ), 'E', 'OFG', 78);
        qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;
END;

/* CGRI$POST_QUERY */
BEGIN
  CGRI$CMP_PK_SAVE;
EXCEPTION
  WHEN OTHERS THEN
    CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
END;

/* CGFK$RESET_BLOCK_WHERE_CLAUSE */
BEGIN
  IF (CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.CMP_WHERE <> 'first_time') THEN
    set_block_property('CMP', DEFAULT_WHERE, CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.CMP_WHERE);
    CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.CMP_WHERE := 'first_time';
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$DEFAULT_WHERE */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    block_id   Block := find_block('CMP');
    sub_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    def_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    r_string   VARCHAR2(512) := NULL;

    FUNCTION add_and(
      P_WHERE IN VARCHAR2
    ) RETURN VARCHAR2 IS
    BEGIN
      IF (nvl( length(P_WHERE), 0) != 0) THEN
        RETURN( P_WHERE || ' and ');
      ELSE
        RETURN( P_WHERE );
      END IF;
    END;

  BEGIN
    IF ( CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.CMP_WHERE = 'first_time') THEN
      CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.CMP_WHERE := get_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE);
    END IF;
    def_where := CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.CMP_WHERE;

    sub_where := NULL;
    r_string := NAME_IN('CMP.NOMBRE');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    IF (sub_where IS NOT NULL) THEN
      def_where := add_and( def_where ) || '((TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO, TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO) in '||'(select EMP_CODIGO, TPOCMP_CODIGO '||'from VISTA_TIPOS_COMPROBANTES where '|| sub_where || '))';
    END IF;

    set_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE, def_where);

  EXCEPTION
    WHEN VALUE_ERROR THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(33, 'Los criterios de consulta son demasiado complejos. Simplifíquelos y vuelva a realizar la consulta.'), 'E', 'OFG', 33);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END;
END;

    Habilitar_Estado_Comprobante;

      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_EXTRANJERA:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_EXTRANJERA;
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_LOCAL:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL;
    ELSE
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_EXTRANJERA:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL;
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_LOCAL:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_EXTRANJERA;
    END IF;

  END IF;

BEGIN

     :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS='QUERY' THEN

    Estado_Boton_Cheque(PROPERTY_FALSE);

DECLARE
  nMvmBlq BLOCK:=FIND_BLOCK('MVM');
  nAscCmpBlq BLOCK:=FIND_BLOCK('ASCCMP');
BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('NEW','INSERT') THEN
-- Cuando se crea un comprobante habilitamos los detalles del comprobante
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,DELETE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  ELSIF :CMP.VMOD_FECHA='V' THEN
-- Si se modifico la fecha, no permitimos modificar los detalles
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,DELETE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  ELSIF NVL(:CMP.VMOD_FECHA,'F')='F' AND :CMP.ESTADO='N' THEN
-- Si no modifico la fecha y no esta cerrado el mes permitimos modificar los detalles
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,DELETE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  END IF;
END;

     - Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     - Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     - Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    No
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          PRE-INSERT
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

BEGIN
  Verificar_Cuadre;
  IF :CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE=1 THEN
-- Si es la formula clave 1, es una secuencia
    IF :CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA IS NOT NULL THEN
      BEGIN
        BEGIN
          GNRL.ACTUALIZA_SECUENCIA(:CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA,:CMP.CLAVE);
        EXCEPTION
          WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
            qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(3, 'No hay ninguna fila en la tabla <p1>', 'CG_CODE_CONTROLS' ), 'F', 'OFG', 3);
            qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
          WHEN TOO_MANY_ROWS THEN
            qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(29, 'Más de un código controla la fila para el dominio especificado', :CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA ), 'F', 'OFG', 29);
            qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
          WHEN OTHERS THEN
            CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
        END;
      END;
    ELSE
      qms$errors.show_message ( 'CNT-00012',:CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA);
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;
/* CGFK$CLR_FK_ON_INS */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NULL AND name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLRLU_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_F;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$VALD_FK_ON_INS */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGFK$CHK_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK(:CMP.NOMBRE_REPORTE ,:CMP.OBLIGACIONES ,:CMP.RETENCIONES ,:CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA ,:CMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD ,:CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE ,:CMP.NOMBRE ,:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push('Tipo de Comprobante no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  ELSE
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(78, 'Debe especificar <p1>', 'Comprobante' ), 'E', 'OFG', 78);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
  NUEVO_COMPROBANTE_FILA;
END;

     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      No
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          ON-ERROR
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

      IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
        IF (constraint_name = 'CMP_TPOCMPEMP_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('Tipo de comprobante no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSIF (constraint_name = 'CMP_CRRMES_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(13, 'Este <p1> no existe', 'CRRMES_MES,TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO' ), 'E', 'OFG', 13);
        ELSE
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      IF (server_err = 2292) THEN
        IF (err_code = 40509) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          KEY-HELP
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          WHEN-CREATE-RECORD
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGNV$RESTRICT_NEW */
BEGIN
  IF (:PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE != 'NORMAL') THEN
    IF(:PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP IS NOT NULL) THEN
      :CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO := :PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP;
    END IF;
    IF(:PARAMETER.PDFECHA IS NOT NULL) THEN
      :CMP.FECHA := to_date(:PARAMETER.PDFECHA);
    END IF;
    IF(:PARAMETER.PNCLAVE IS NOT NULL) THEN
      :CMP.CLAVE := to_number(:PARAMETER.PNCLAVE);
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
  :CMP.INICIO_BALANCE:=TO_DATE(:GLOBAL.INICIO_BALANCE,'DD/MM/YYYY HH24:MI');
  :CMP.FINAL_BALANCE:=TO_DATE(:GLOBAL.FINAL_BALANCE,'DD/MM/YYYY HH24:MI');
  :CMP.MAYORIZADO:='F';
END;

BEGIN
-- Hacemos rollback para deshacer cualquier POST que se ha hecho con programación
  HACER_ROLLBACK('ENTER-QUERY');
END;

     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      No
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------

     - Subclass Information

     * Trigger Text                                  

BEGIN
  IF (:MVM.CANTIDAD_MOVIMIENTOS>1
     OR (:MVM.CANTIDAD_MOVIMIENTOS=1 AND :MVM.CODIGO_PLAN IS NOT NULL))
     OR (:RTN.CANTIDAD_RETENCIONES>1
     OR (:RTN.CANTIDAD_RETENCIONES=1 AND :RTN.L_EMP_DIRECCION IS NOT NULL))THEN
-- Si hay movimientos descapacitamos el campo de tipos de comprobantes
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  ELSE
-- Si no hay movimientos descapacitamos el campo de tipos de comprobantes
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO',ENABLED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO',NAVIGABLE,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
-- Siempre habilitamos un campo de la asociacion para que no de errores al ver otros comprobantes
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('ASCCMP.DOCUMENTO',ENABLED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('ASCCMP.DOCUMENTO',NAVIGABLE,PROPERTY_TRUE);
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      No
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes

     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          WHEN-VALIDATE-ITEM
     - Subclass Information

     * Trigger Text                                  

BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.MODE='QUERY' AND :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_ITEM='CMP.CGRI$TPOCMP_CODIGO' THEN
/* Si el campo es la copia del tipo de comprobante codigo, marcamos el registro
   como no actualizado porque ese campo solo es para guardar la copia de la
   clave primaria y no importa si se ha cambiado */
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'CMP', STATUS ,QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
   qms$event_item('WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE');

/* CGNV$ENTER_QUERY_PARAMS */
BEGIN
  IF ((:SYSTEM.MODE = 'ENTER-QUERY') AND
      (CGNV$.nav_enter_query = FALSE) AND
      (:PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE != 'NORMAL')) THEN
    CGNV$.nav_enter_query := TRUE;
    IF(:PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP IS NOT NULL) THEN
      :CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO := :PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP;
    END IF;
    IF(:PARAMETER.PDFECHA IS NOT NULL) THEN
      :CMP.FECHA := to_date(:PARAMETER.PDFECHA);
    END IF;
    IF(:PARAMETER.PNCLAVE IS NOT NULL) THEN
      :CMP.CLAVE := to_number(:PARAMETER.PNCLAVE);
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;
       - Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    Yes
       ^ Execution Hierarchy                         Before
       - Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  No
       - 'Keyboard Help' Text                        
       - Trigger Steps                               
       ----------
       * Name                                        WHEN-VALIDATE-ITEM
       - Subclass Information                        
       - Comments                                    
       - Trigger Style                               PL/SQL
       * Trigger Text                                

BEGIN
  :CMP.CLAVE:=NULL;
  :ASCCMP.ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2:=NULL;
  IF :CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE=1 THEN
-- Si 1 solo maneja secuencia que no se puede modificar
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',REQUIRED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  ELSIF :CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE=2 THEN
-- Si 2 maneja fecha + una secuencia que es ingresable
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',REQUIRED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',ENABLED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',NAVIGABLE,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    :CMP.CLAVE:=Encontrar_Secuencia(:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO,:CMP.FECHA);
  ELSE
-- Si 3 maneja solo fecha
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',REQUIRED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    :CMP.CLAVE:=1;
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('CMP.CLAVE',ENABLED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  END IF;
  IF :CMP.RETENCIONES='V' THEN
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('RTN',INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('RTN',UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  ELSE
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('RTN',INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('RTN',UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  END IF;
END;
/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NULL AND name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLRLU_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_F;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
      IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.CLAVE') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.FECHA') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (name_in('CMP.CLAVE') IS NOT NULL AND name_in('CMP.FECHA') IS NOT NULL AND name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_CMP_PK(:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.FECHA ,:CMP.CLAVE ,:CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.ROWID);
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(6, 'Ya existe una fila con idéntico <p1>', 'Código,Número,Fecha,Comprobante' ), 'W', 'OFG', 6);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
      ELSE
          qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(78, 'Debe especificar <p1>', 'Número,Fecha,Comprobante' ), 'E', 'OFG', 78);
          qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      END IF;
END;
       * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    No
       * Execution Hierarchy                         Override
       * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  Yes
       - 'Keyboard Help' Text                        
       - Trigger Steps                               
       ----------
       * Name                                        KEY-HELP
       - Subclass Information                        
       - Comments                                    
       - Trigger Style                               PL/SQL
       * Trigger Text                                

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
  VERIFICAR_FECHA_COMPROBANTE;
END;

BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.MODE='NORMAL' AND :CMP.CGRI$FECHA!=:CMP.FECHA AND :CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE=2 THEN
-- Encontramos una nueva secuencia solo si al actualizar es una fecha distinta a la original
    :CMP.CLAVE:=Encontrar_Secuencia(:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO,:CMP.FECHA);
  END IF;
END;

DECLARE
  nMvmBlq BLOCK:=FIND_BLOCK('MVM');
  nAscCmpBlq BLOCK:=FIND_BLOCK('ASCCMP');
BEGIN
-- SI MODIFICAN LA FECHA NO PUEDEN MODIFICAR LOS MOVIMIENTOS SIN GRABAR PRIMERO LOS CAMBIOS
  IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('CHANGED') THEN
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nMvmBlq,DELETE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,INSERT_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(nAscCmpBlq,UPDATE_ALLOWED,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    :CMP.VMOD_FECHA:='V'; -- Marcamos como modificado el registro
    QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('CNT-00052');
  END IF;
END;
/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
    IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.CLAVE') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.FECHA') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (name_in('CMP.CLAVE') IS NOT NULL AND name_in('CMP.FECHA') IS NOT NULL AND name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_CMP_PK(:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.FECHA ,:CMP.CLAVE ,:CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.ROWID);
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(6, 'Ya existe una fila con idéntico <p1>', 'Código,Número,Fecha,Comprobante' ), 'W', 'OFG', 6);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
    ELSE
        qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(78, 'Debe especificar <p1>', 'Número,Fecha,Comprobante' ), 'E', 'OFG', 78);
        qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;
END;

       * Execution Hierarchy                         Override
       * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  Yes

       - Trigger Steps                               
       ----------
       * Name                                        KEY-HELP
       - Subclass Information                        
       - Comments                                    
       - Trigger Style                               PL/SQL
       * Trigger Text

/* CGUV$CHK_KEYS_ON_VAL_FLD */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.CLAVE') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.FECHA') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  IF (name_in('CMP.CLAVE') IS NOT NULL AND name_in('CMP.FECHA') IS NOT NULL AND name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGUV$CHK_CMP_PK(:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.FECHA ,:CMP.CLAVE ,:CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO ,:CMP.ROWID);
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(6, 'Ya existe una fila con idéntico <p1>', 'Código,Número,Fecha,Comprobante' ), 'W', 'OFG', 6);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN NULL;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
  ELSE
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(78, 'Debe especificar <p1>', 'Número,Fecha,Comprobante' ), 'E', 'OFG', 78);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END IF;
END;

       - Trigger Steps

       * Name                                        KEY-HELP

DECLARE
  vDesc COMPROBANTES.CONCEPTOTYPE:=:CMP.CONCEPTO;
BEGIN
  VERIFICAR_FECHA_COMPROBANTE;
  IF GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('MVM',STATUS)!='QUERY' THEN
-- si se ha modificado los movimientos, automaticamente no permitimos modificar el estado del comprobante
    :CMP.ESTADO:=:CMP.ESTADO_ANTERIOR;
    QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('CNT-00042');
  ELSE
-- Estado anterior almacena el valor original del estado del comprobante
    IF :CMP.ESTADO='C' THEN
-- No dejamos fijar cerrado desde los comprobantes
      :CMP.ESTADO:=:CMP.ESTADO_ANTERIOR;
      QMS$ERRORS.SHOW_MESSAGE('No se puede fijar el estado de Cerrado directamente');
    ELSE
      :CMP.ESTADO_ANTERIOR:=:CMP.ESTADO;
      Habilitar_Deshabilitar_Bloques;
      :CMP.ESTADO_MODIFICADO:='V';
-- Mandamos a enviar los cambios a la BD sin grabarlos todavia ni que se genere
-- ni modifique las retenciones
      QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.ADD_SUPPRESS_MESSAGE('FRM-40404'); -- No mostramos el mensaje de grabado
      POST;
      QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.DELETE_SUPPRESS_MESSAGE('FRM-40404');
      :CMP.ESTADO:=:CMP.ESTADO; -- Marcamos como modificado el bloque de comprobantes
      IF :CMP.ESTADO='N' THEN
-- Reconsultamos los movimientos del comprobante si el estado vuelve a ser normal
        RECONSULTAR_HIJOS;
        :MVM.SECUENCIA:=:MVM.SECUENCIA; -- Marcamos como modificado los hijos, y por lo tanto el padre
      END IF;
/*      :CMP.CONCEPTO:=NVL(vDesc,' ')||' ';
      :CMP.CONCEPTO:=vDesc; -- solo para que registre como modificado el estado*/
    END IF;
  END IF;
EXCEPTION
  WHEN FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE THEN
    :CMP.ESTADO:=:CMP.ESTADO_ANTERIOR; -- dejamos el estado anterior
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(TO_NUMBER(GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('CMP',CURRENT_RECORD)),'CMP',STATUS,QUERY_STATUS);
    RAISE;
END;
       * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    No
       * Execution Hierarchy                         Override
       * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  Yes
       - 'Keyboard Help' Text                        
       - Trigger Steps

/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NULL AND name_in('CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLRLU_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_F;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

begin

BEGIN
--  :CMP.VALIDAR:='F'; -- no validamos la asociaciones al consultar
-- LEEMOS LA MASCARA DE LAS ASOCIACIONES
  SELECT MASCARA
    INTO :ASCCMP.MASCARA
    FROM ASOCIACIONES_TIPO_DE_COMPROBAN
    WHERE TPOCMP_CODIGO=:ASCCMP.ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2 AND
          NOMBRE=:ASCCMP.ASCTPOCMP_NOMBRE;
  VALIDAR_ASCCMP;
  SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, STATUS ,QUERY_STATUS);
  SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('CMP',CURRENT_RECORD),'CMP', STATUS ,QUERY_STATUS);
END;

/* CGFK$VALD_FK_ON_INS */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('ASCCMP.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('ASCCMP.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('ASCCMP.ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('ASCCMP.CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGFK$CHK_ASCCMP_ASCCMP_CMP_FK(:ASCCMP.CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO ,:ASCCMP.CMP_CLAVE ,:ASCCMP.ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2 ,:ASCCMP.CMP_FECHA);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(13, 'Este <p1> no existe', 'Fecha,Código,Clave,Código' ), 'E', 'OFG', 13);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      No
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          ON-ERROR
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

      IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
        IF (constraint_name = 'ASCCMP_ASCTPOCMP_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(13, 'Este <p1> no existe', 'Código,Asctpocmp Nombre' ), 'E', 'OFG', 13);
        ELSE
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      IF (server_err = 2292) THEN
        IF (err_code = 40509) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (41105, 41106) ) THEN
      IF (err_code = 41105) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(35, 'La consulta de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Comprobante','Comprobantes' ), 'E', 'OFG', 35);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    ELSIF (err_code = 41106) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(36, 'La inserción de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Comprobante','Comprobantes' ), 'E', 'OFG', 36);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          KEY-HELP
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          KEY-CLRREC
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

BEGIN
-- No permitimos limpiar el registro en las asociaciones de comprobantes
-- salvo que la asociacion este en nula
  IF :ASCCMP.ASCTPOCMP_NOMBRE IS NULL THEN
    CLEAR_RECORD;
  ELSE
    NULL;
  END IF;
END;

     * Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes

     ----------
     * Name                                          WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE
     - Subclass Information

     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text

END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGCD$POST_INSERT */
BEGIN
  BEGIN
    CGCD$SYNC_SRVR_MVM;
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
END;

BEGIN
-- Si al grabar un movimiento este tiene un cheque asociado, habilitamos el boton de cheques
  HABILITAR_CHEQUES;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_LOOKUP_DATA */
BEGIN
  IF (    name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.S_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK(
        :MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA
       ,:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2
       ,:MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2
       ,:MVM.CUENTA2
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.S_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO            );
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('No se puede borrar una Cuenta con movimientos', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'MVM', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
  IF (    name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_S_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.SS_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL
      OR name_in('MVM.S_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK(
        :MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA_PLN
       ,:MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1
       ,:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO
       ,:MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
       ,:MVM.NOMBRE
       ,:MVM.CODIGO_PLAN
       ,:MVM.S_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
       ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('Cuenta del plan de cuentas no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'MVM', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$RESET_BLOCK_WHERE_CLAUSE */
BEGIN
  IF (CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.MVM_WHERE <> 'first_time') THEN
    set_block_property('MVM', DEFAULT_WHERE, CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.MVM_WHERE);
    CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.MVM_WHERE := 'first_time';
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
-- Poblamos los campos del debe y haber
  :MVM.HABERM:=0;
  :MVM.DEBEM:=0;
  IF :MVM.MONEDA!=:CMP.MONEDA_LOCAL THEN
    :MVM.DEBEM:=:MVM.DEBEE;
    :MVM.HABERM:=:MVM.HABERE;
  ELSE
    :MVM.DEBEM:=:MVM.DEBE;
    :MVM.HABERM:=:MVM.HABER;
  END IF;
  :MVM.MONEDA_LOCAL:=:CMP.MONEDA_LOCAL;
--  Fijar_Asociacion;
  :MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS:=:MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1;
-- La moneda de trabajo para modificar sera la que fue grabada
  :MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO:=:MVM.MONEDA;
END;

DECLARE
  nTemp NUMBER;
BEGIN
-- Fijamos el tipo de dato en retencion si cambiar el valor del movimiento
  IF :CMP.RETENCIONES IN ('V','R') THEN
    nTemp:=CALCULAR_MOVIMIENTOS_RTN(:MVM.CODIGO_PLAN,NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_FACTURADO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_POR_UNO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_POR_CINCO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_IVA_FACTURADO,0),NVL(:CMP.NIVA_COMPRAS,0),NVL(:CMP.NIVA_SERVICIOS,0));
  END IF;
  SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, :SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK, STATUS ,QUERY_STATUS);
END;

DECLARE
  nReg NUMBER:=:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD;
  CURSOR cObl IS
    SELECT tipo
    FROM OBLIGACIONES
    WHERE obl_id=:MVM.OBL_OBL_ID;
  vTipoObl OBLIGACIONES.TIPOTYPE;
BEGIN
-- Deshabilitamos el debe o el haber si el movimiento
-- tiene una obligación asociada. Se deshabilita el debe
-- si el movimiento con obligación esta en el haber
-- y se deshabilita el haber si el movimiento con obligación
-- esta en el debe
  IF :MVM.OBL_OBL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN
    OPEN cObl;
    FETCH cObl INTO vTipoObl;
    CLOSE cObl;
    IF vTipoObl='P' THEN
-- Si entra aqui es cuenta por pagar
      IF :MVM.HABERM>0 THEN
-- Si el movimiento es de haber (creo la deuda), no dejamos actualizar debe
        SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.DEBEM',nREg,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
      ELSE
-- Si el movimiento es del debe (paga la deuda), no dejamos actualizar haber
        SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.HABERM',nREg,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
      END IF;
    ELSE
-- si entra aqui es porque es cuenta por cobrar
      IF :MVM.HABERM>0 THEN
-- Si el movimiento es de haber (pago la deuda), no dejamos actualizar debe
        SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.DEBEM',nREg,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
      ELSE
-- Si el movimiento es del debe (paga la deuda), no dejamos actualizar haber
        SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.HABERM',nREg,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
      END IF;
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
  HABILITAR_CHEQUES;
END;

    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;

/* CGFK$PQ_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.CUENTA2') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  IF (name_in('MVM.CODIGO_PLAN') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$DEFAULT_WHERE */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    block_id   Block := find_block('MVM');
    sub_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    def_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    r_string   VARCHAR2(512) := NULL;

    FUNCTION add_and(
      P_WHERE IN VARCHAR2
    ) RETURN VARCHAR2 IS
    BEGIN
      IF (nvl( length(P_WHERE), 0) != 0) THEN
        RETURN( P_WHERE || ' and ');
      ELSE
        RETURN( P_WHERE );
      END IF;
    END;

  BEGIN
    IF ( CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.MVM_WHERE = 'first_time') THEN
      CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.MVM_WHERE := get_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE);
    END IF;
    def_where := CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.MVM_WHERE;

    sub_where := NULL;
    r_string := NAME_IN('MVM.CUENTA2');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(NOMBRE ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    IF (sub_where IS NOT NULL) THEN
      def_where := add_and( def_where ) || '((SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO, SS_S_A_CODIGO, SS_S_CODIGO, SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO, SS_CODIGO, SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO, S_CODIGO, SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO) in '||'(select S_S_A_SC_CODIGO, S_S_A_CODIGO,
          S_S_CODIGO, S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO, S_CODIGO, S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO, CODIGO, S_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO '||'from SUBAUXILIARES_3 where '|| sub_where || '))';
    END IF;

    sub_where := NULL;
    r_string := NAME_IN('MVM.CODIGO_PLAN');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(CODIGO '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(CODIGO '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(CODIGO like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(CODIGO ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    IF (sub_where IS NOT NULL) THEN
      def_where := add_and( def_where ) || '((SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO, SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO, SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO, SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO, SS_S_A_CODIGO, SS_S_CODIGO, SS_CODIGO, S_CODIGO) in '||'(select EMP_CODIGO, MYR_CODIGO,
          CNT_CODIGO, SCNT_CODIGO, AXL_CODIGO, SAXL_CODIGO, SAXL2_CODIGO, SAXL3_CODIGO '||'from PLAN_DE_CUENTAS where '|| sub_where || '))';
    END IF;

    set_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE, def_where);

  EXCEPTION
    WHEN VALUE_ERROR THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(33, 'Los criterios de consulta son demasiado complejos. Simplifíquelos y vuelva a realizar la consulta.'), 'E', 'OFG', 33);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END;
END;

BEGIN
-- Fijamos el estado del registro al entrar en el mismo
  :MVM.ESTADO_REGISTRO:=:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS;
END;

BEGIN
  IF :CMP.NUEVO_MOVIMIENTO='F' THEN
    Fijar_Asociacion;
    DESHABILITAR_DEBE_HABER_MVM;
  ELSE
    :CMP.NUEVO_MOVIMIENTO:='F';
    CLEAR_RECORD;
    :MVM.SECUENCIA:=1;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
-- Mostramos la moneda local para los totales
  IF :SYSTEM.MODE='NORMAL' THEN
    IF :CMP.MONEDA_LOCAL=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL THEN
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_EXTRANJERA:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_EXTRANJERA;
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_LOCAL:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL;
    ELSE
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_EXTRANJERA:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL;
      :MVM.MVM_MONEDA_LOCAL:=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_EXTRANJERA;
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;

DECLARE
-- Descapacita el boton de las obligaciones si ya tiene una obligacón asociada
-- o si el tipo de comprobante maneja obligacione en el haber
-- Descapacita la modificacion del codigo del plan de cuentas
-- si el movimiento ha generado obligaciones
  nPropiedad NUMBER;
  nRegistro NUMBER:=TO_NUMBER(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD);
BEGIN
  IF (:CMP.OBLIGACIONES IN ('P','C') AND :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('INSERT','NEW')) AND
     (:MVM.OBL_OBL_ID IS NULL) THEN
    nPropiedad:=PROPERTY_TRUE;
  ELSE
    nPropiedad:=PROPERTY_FALSE;
  END IF;
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.BTNOBL',ENABLED,nPropiedad);
  SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.BTNOBL',NAVIGABLE,nPropiedad);
  IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS NOT IN ('INSERT','NEW') AND :MVM.OBL_OBL_ID IS NOT NULL THEN
-- Si esta actualizando el registro solo puede actualizarse desde la ventana de obligaciones
    SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.CODIGO_PLAN',nRegistro,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.CUENTA2',nRegistro,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    IF :MVM.DEBEM=0 THEN
-- Descapacitamos el debe o el haber dependiendo el qie tiene valor diferente de cero
      SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.DEBEM',nRegistro,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    ELSE
      SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY('MVM.HABERM',nRegistro,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;

DECLARE
  nReg NUMBER:=TO_NUMBER(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD);
BEGIN
  if :MVM.ESTADO_REGISTRO='NEW' THEN
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(nReg,'MVM',STATUS,NEW_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN

    :MVM.OBL_OBL_ID:=NULL;

/* CGFK$CLR_FK_ON_INS */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.CUENTA2') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  IF (name_in('MVM.CODIGO_PLAN') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$VALD_FK_ON_INS */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.CUENTA2') IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        CGFK$LKP_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK(
          TRUE
         ,:MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA
         ,:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2
         ,:MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2
         ,:MVM.S_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO);
      EXCEPTION
        WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('No se puede borrar una Cuenta con movimientos', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
          qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
        WHEN OTHERS THEN
          CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
      END;
  END IF;
  IF (name_in('MVM.CODIGO_PLAN') IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        CGFK$LKP_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK(
          TRUE
         ,:MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA_PLN
         ,:MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1
         ,:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO
         ,:MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
         ,:MVM.NOMBRE
         ,:MVM.S_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
         ,:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO);
      EXCEPTION
        WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('Cuenta del plan de cuentas no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
          qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
        WHEN OTHERS THEN
          CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
      END;
  END IF;
  IF (name_in('MVM.CMP_FECHA') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('MVM.CMP_CLAVE') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('MVM.CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('MVM.CMP_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
  BEGIN
    CGFK$CHK_MVM_MVM_CMP_FK(:MVM.CMP_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO ,:MVM.CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO ,:MVM.CMP_FECHA ,:MVM.CMP_CLAVE);
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push('Comprobante no existente.', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
      CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGUI$GET_UNIQUE_ID */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.MVM_ID') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGUI$GET_NEXT_MVM_SEQ(:MVM.MVM_ID);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(3, 'No hay ninguna fila en la tabla <p1>', 'SYS.DUAL' ), 'F', 'OFG', 3);
        qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      WHEN TOO_MANY_ROWS THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(24, 'Hay más de una fila en la tabla <p1>', 'SYS.DUAL' ), 'F', 'OFG', 24);
        qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

DECLARE
  vTemp VARCHAR2(2000):=:CMP.CONCEPTO;
BEGIN
-- Marcamos como modificada la cabecera para que se procesen cuelquier
-- cambio que se halla hecho al detalle especialmente si tiene retenciones
  :CMP.CONCEPTO:=NVL(:CMP.CONCEPTO,' ')||' ';
  :CMP.CONCEPTO:=vTemp;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      No
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          ON-ERROR
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

      IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
        IF (constraint_name = 'MVM_SAXL3_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('No se puede borrar una Cuenta con movimientos', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSIF (constraint_name = 'MVM_OBL_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(13, 'Este <p1> no existe', 'Obl Id' ), 'E', 'OFG', 13);
        ELSE
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      IF (server_err = 2292) THEN
        IF (err_code = 40510) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSIF (err_code = 40509) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (41105, 41106) ) THEN
      IF (err_code = 41105) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(35, 'La consulta de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Movimientos','Comprobantes' ), 'E', 'OFG', 35);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    ELSIF (err_code = 41106) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(36, 'La inserción de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Movimientos','Comprobantes' ), 'E', 'OFG', 36);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          KEY-HELP
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('INSERT','NEW') THEN
-- Solo cuando se inserta o se crea un registro deja limpiar
    CLEAR_RECORD;
  END IF;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      No
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          WHEN-VALIDATE-RECORD
     - Subclass Information

     * Trigger Text                                  

BEGIN
  IF :MVM.DEBE>0 AND :MVM.HABER>0 THEN
    qms$errors.show_message ( p_mesg => 'CNT-00010');
  END IF;
  IF :SYSTEM.MODE='QUERY' THEN
-- Consultando el bloque fijamos el registro como no modificado
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD,'MVM',STATUS,QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

DECLARE
  nRecCmp NUMBER:=TO_NUMBER(GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY('CMP',CURRENT_RECORD));
  nCmpFechaItm ITEM:=FIND_ITEM('CMP.FECHA');
BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS='CHANGED' THEN
-- si se modifica los movimientos deshabilitamos que pueda modificar la fecha del comprobante
    SET_ITEM_INSTANCE_PROPERTY(nCmpFechaItm,nRecCmp,UPDATEABLE,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  END IF;
END;

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
   qms$event_item('WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE');
end;

BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.MODE='NORMAL'
    AND GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK,STATUS)!='NEW'
    AND GET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD,'MVM',STATUS)='INSERT' AND :CMP.NUEVO_MOVIMIENTO='F'
    AND get_block_property('cmp',status)='CHANGED' THEN
    QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.ADD_SUPPRESS_MESSAGE('FRM-41803'); -- Quitamos el mensaje que no exite un registro anterior
    DUPLICATE_ITEM;
    QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.DELETE_SUPPRESS_MESSAGE('FRM-41803'); -- Dejamos el mensaje normal
  ELSE
    :CMP.NUEVO_MOVIMIENTO:='F';
  END IF;
END;

    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

       - Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    Yes
       ^ Execution Hierarchy                         Before
       - Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  No
       - 'Keyboard Help' Text                        
       - Trigger Steps                               
       ----------
       * Name                                        WHEN-VALIDATE-ITEM
       - Subclass Information                        
       - Comments                                    
       - Trigger Style                               PL/SQL
       * Trigger Text                                

BEGIN
-- Asignamos el nombre de la cuenta si es diferente
  IF :MVM.CUENTA2 IS NULL OR :MVM.CUENTA2!=:MVM.NOMBRE THEN
    :MVM.CUENTA2:=:MVM.NOMBRE;
    :MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2:=:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO;
    :MVM.MONEDA:=:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2;
    IF :SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS IN ('INSERT','NEW') THEN
-- Si el registro no esta grabado en la base de datos enceramos el debe y el haber
      :MVM.DEBE:=0;
      :MVM.HABER:=0;
      :MVM.DEBEE:=0;
      :MVM.HABERE:=0;
      :MVM.DEBEM:=0;
      :MVM.HABERM:=0;
    END IF;
    :MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS:=:MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1;
    Fijar_Asociacion;
    IF :CMP.RETENCIONES='V' THEN
      :MVM.HABERM:=CALCULAR_MOVIMIENTOS_RTN(:MVM.CODIGO_PLAN,NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_FACTURADO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_POR_UNO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_POR_CINCO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_IVA_FACTURADO,0),NVL(:CMP.NIVA_COMPRAS,0),NVL(:CMP.NIVA_SERVICIOS,0));
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;
/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.CODIGO_PLAN') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  list_values;
END;

BEGIN
  IF :MVM.CODIGO_PLAN IS NOT NULL THEN
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.CUENTA2',VALIDATE_FROM_LIST,PROPERTY_FALSE);
  ELSE
    SET_ITEM_PROPERTY('MVM.CUENTA2',VALIDATE_FROM_LIST,PROPERTY_TRUE);
  END IF;

DECLARE
  vCodPlan VARCHAR2(200):=
           :MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO||:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO||
           :MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO||:MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO||:MVM.SS_S_CODIGO||
           :MVM.SS_CODIGO||:MVM.S_CODIGO;
BEGIN
-- Asignamos el nombre de la cuenta si es diferente
  vCodPlan:=REPLACE(vCodPlan,'00000','');
  IF :MVM.CODIGO_PLAN IS NULL OR :MVM.CODIGO_PLAN!=vCodPlan THEN
    :MVM.CODIGO_PLAN:=vCodPlan;
    :MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO:=:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2;
    :MVM.MONEDA:=:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2;
    :MVM.DEBE:=0;
    :MVM.HABER:=0;
    :MVM.DEBEE:=0;
    :MVM.HABERE:=0;
    :MVM.DEBEM:=0;
    :MVM.HABERM:=0;
    VALIDATE(RECORD_SCOPE);
    :MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS:=:MVM.ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1;
    Fijar_Asociacion;
  END IF;
  IF :CMP.RETENCIONES='V' THEN
    :MVM.HABERM:=CALCULAR_MOVIMIENTOS_RTN(:MVM.CODIGO_PLAN,NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_FACTURADO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_POR_UNO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_POR_CINCO,0),NVL(:CMP.NTOTAL_IVA_FACTURADO,0),NVL(:CMP.NIVA_COMPRAS,0),NVL(:CMP.NIVA_SERVICIOS,0));
  END IF;
END;
/* CGFK$WVI_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.CUENTA2') IS NULL) THEN
    IF (:SYSTEM.RECORD_STATUS = 'NEW') THEN
      RETURN;
    END IF;
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
       * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    No
       * Execution Hierarchy                         Override
       * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  Yes
       - 'Keyboard Help' Text                        
       - Trigger Steps                               
       ----------
       * Name                                        KEY-LISTVAL
       - Subclass Information                        
       - Comments                                    
       - Trigger Style                               PL/SQL
       * Trigger Text                                

/* CGFK$KL_CLR_DEPS_OVF */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('MVM.CUENTA2') IS NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK;
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
  list_values;
END;
       * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    Yes
       * Execution Hierarchy                         Before
       * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                  Yes

       - Trigger Steps

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';

      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);

        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

begin
   qms$event_item('WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE');
end;

BEGIN
  IF :SYSTEM.MODE='NORMAL' AND GET_BLOCK_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_BLOCK,STATUS)!='NEW'
    AND :MVM.DESCRIPCION IS NULL THEN
      qms$forms_errors.Add_Suppress_Message ('FRM-41803');
      DUPLICATE_ITEM;
      qms$forms_errors.delete_Suppress_Message ('FRM-41803');
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

      IF :CMP.OBLIGACIONES='P' THEN
        :GLOBAL.TITULO_OBLIGACIONES:='Cuentas por Pagar';
      ELSE
        :GLOBAL.TITULO_OBLIGACIONES:='Cuentas por Cobrar';
      END IF;
      PAGAR_OBLIGACIONES(:MVM.CODIGO_PLAN,:MVM.DEBEM,:MVM.OBL_OBL_ID);
    END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
   qms$event_item('WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE');
end;

BEGIN
-- Si el estado del comprobante es Normal, siempre va al siguiente registro
-- salvo que el comprobante este Cerrado va al siguiente registro salvo
-- que este en el ultimo registro
  IF :CMP.ESTADO='N' THEN
    NEXT_RECORD;
  ELSIF :SYSTEM.LAST_RECORD='FALSE' THEN
    NEXT_RECORD;
  ELSE
    NEXT_BLOCK;
  END IF;
END;

        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;

begin

BEGIN
-- Fijamos el proveedor despues de consultar la BD si el tipo es Otro
  VALIDAR_TIPO_RETENIDO;
  IF :RTN.TIPO='O' THEN
    :RTN.L_PRD_NOMBRE:=:RTN.RETENIDO_A;
    :RTN.L_PRD_RUC:=:RTN.RUC;
  END IF;
END;
/* CGFK$QRY_LOOKUP_DATA */
BEGIN
  IF (name_in('RTN.EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL OR name_in('RTN.TPORTN_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_VSTTPSRTN_FK(:RTN.VSTTPSRTN_TPORTN_VALOR ,:RTN.TPORTNEMP_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA ,:RTN.DESCRIPCION ,:RTN.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD ,:RTN.FORMULA_IVA ,:RTN.FORMULA_RETENCION ,:RTN.EMP_CODIGO ,:RTN.TPORTN_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('Tipo de retención no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'RTN', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
  IF (name_in('RTN.PRD_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_PRD_FK(:RTN.L_PRD_PLNCTA_CODIGO ,:RTN.L_PRD_RUC ,:RTN.L_PRD_NOMBRE ,:RTN.PRD_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('Proveedor no existente.', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'RTN', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
  IF (name_in('RTN.EMP_CODIGO') IS NOT NULL) THEN
    BEGIN
      CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_EMP_FK(
        :RTN.L_PRV_PROVINCIA
       ,:RTN.L_CNT_CANTON
       ,:RTN.L_PRQ_PARROQUIA
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_PRQ_CODIGO
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_PRQ_CNT_CODIGO
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_PRQ_CNT_PRV_CODIGO
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_DIRECCION
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_RUC
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_TELEFONO
       ,:RTN.L_EMP_DESCRIPCION
       ,:RTN.EMP_CODIGO              );
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push('Empresa no existente', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
    SET_RECORD_PROPERTY(:SYSTEM.TRIGGER_RECORD, 'RTN', STATUS ,                 QUERY_STATUS);
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$RESET_BLOCK_WHERE_CLAUSE */

  IF (CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.RTN_WHERE <> 'first_time') THEN
    set_block_property('RTN', DEFAULT_WHERE, CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.RTN_WHERE);
    CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.RTN_WHERE := 'first_time';
  END IF;
END;
