/* CGFK$DEFAULT_WHERE */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    block_id   Block := find_block('RTN');
    sub_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    def_where  VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;
    r_string   VARCHAR2(512) := NULL;

    FUNCTION add_and(
      P_WHERE IN VARCHAR2
    ) RETURN VARCHAR2 IS
    BEGIN
      IF (nvl( length(P_WHERE), 0) != 0) THEN
        RETURN( P_WHERE || ' and ');
      ELSE
        RETURN( P_WHERE );
      END IF;
    END;

  BEGIN
    IF ( CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.RTN_WHERE = 'first_time') THEN
      CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.RTN_WHERE := get_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE);
    END IF;
    def_where := CG$CNTINGCMP_GLOBALS.RTN_WHERE;

    sub_where := NULL;
    r_string := NAME_IN('RTN.L_EMP_DESCRIPCION');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DESCRIPCION '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DESCRIPCION '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DESCRIPCION like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DESCRIPCION ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    r_string := NAME_IN('RTN.L_EMP_TELEFONO');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(TELEFONO '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(TELEFONO '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(TELEFONO like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(TELEFONO ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    r_string := NAME_IN('RTN.L_EMP_RUC');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(RUC '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(RUC '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(RUC like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(RUC ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    r_string := NAME_IN('RTN.L_EMP_DIRECCION');
    IF (r_string IS NOT NULL) THEN
      BEGIN
        IF substr(r_string, 1,1) in ('<','>','=') THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DIRECCION '|| r_string || ')';
        ELSIF substr(r_string, 1,1) ='#' THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DIRECCION '|| substr(r_string,2) || ')';
        ELSIF instr(r_string, '') <> 0 THEN
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DIRECCION like '''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        ELSE
          sub_where := add_and( sub_where ) || '(DIRECCION ='''|| replace(r_string,'''','''''') || ''')';
        END IF;
      END;
    END IF;
    IF (sub_where IS NOT NULL) THEN
      def_where := add_and( def_where ) || '((TPORTNEMP_EMP_CODIGO) in '||'(select CODIGO '||'from EMPRESAS where '|| sub_where || '))';
    END IF;

    set_block_property(block_id, DEFAULT_WHERE, def_where);

  EXCEPTION
    WHEN VALUE_ERROR THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(33, 'Los criterios de consulta son demasiado complejos. Simplifíquelos y vuelva a realizar la consulta.'), 'E', 'OFG', 33);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
  END;
END;
     - Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     ^ Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     - Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    No
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps

     * Name                                          WHEN-DATABASE-RECORD

     - Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     - Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     - Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    No
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          ON-ERROR
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

      IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
        IF (constraint_name = 'RTN_PRD_FK') THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push('Proveedor no existente.', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
        ELSE
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      IF (server_err = 2292) THEN
        IF (err_code = 40509) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (41105, 41106) ) THEN
      IF (err_code = 41105) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(35, 'La consulta de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Retenciones','Comprobantes' ), 'E', 'OFG', 35);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    ELSIF (err_code = 41106) THEN
      qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(36, 'La inserción de <p1> debe estar en el contexto de <p2>', 'Retenciones','Comprobantes' ), 'E', 'OFG', 36);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;

    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);

        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;

BEGIN
  VALIDAR_TIPO_RETENIDO;
-- Enceramos el nombre y ruc del proveedor si ya se ha ingresado
-- datos en los campos y se cambia el tipo de proveedor
  IF :RTN.TIPO='O' AND :RTN.PRD_CODIGO IS NOT NULL THEN
    :RTN.L_PRD_NOMBRE:=NULL;
    :RTN.L_PRD_RUC:=NULL;
  ELSIF :RTN.TIPO='P' AND :RTN.PRD_CODIGO IS NULL THEN
    :RTN.L_PRD_NOMBRE:=NULL;
    :RTN.L_PRD_RUC:=NULL;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;

/* CGAP$OLES_SEQUENCE_BEFORE */
begin
  qms$event_data_block('POST-QUERY');
end;

BEGIN
  :OBLCNT.MONEDA:=:MVM.MONEDA; -- copiamos la moneda de trabajo del movimiento
  IF :OBLCNT.MONEDA=:GLOBAL.MONEDA_LOCAL THEN
-- si la moneda es igual a la local, fijamos la deuda que viene de DEBE y HABER
    IF :OBLCNT.TIPO='P' THEN
      :OBLCNT.DEUDA:=:OBLCNT.HABER;
      :OBLCNT.PAGADO:=:OBLCNT.DEBE;
    ELSE
      :OBLCNT.DEUDA:=:OBLCNT.DEBE;
      :OBLCNT.PAGADO:=:OBLCNT.HABER;
    END IF;
  ELSE
-- si la moneda no es igual a la local, fijamos la deuda que viene de DEBEE y HABERE
    IF :OBLCNT.TIPO='P' THEN
      :OBLCNT.DEUDA:=:OBLCNT.HABERE;
      :OBLCNT.PAGADO:=:OBLCNT.DEBEE;
    ELSE
      :OBLCNT.DEUDA:=:OBLCNT.DEBEE;
      :OBLCNT.PAGADO:=:OBLCNT.HABERE;
    END IF;
  END IF;
-- Fijamos, cuanto puede pagar máximo
  :OBLCNT.MAXIMO_PAGO:=:OBLCNT.DEUDA-:OBLCNT.PAGADO;
  :OBLCNT.PAGO:=0;
END;

     - Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     - Execution Hierarchy                           Override
     - Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    No
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          ON-ERROR
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text                                  

/* CGTE$BLK_LEVEL_ERROR_TRAP */
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    err_code        CONSTANT NUMBER         := ERROR_CODE;
    err_type        CONSTANT VARCHAR2(3)    := ERROR_TYPE;
    server_err               NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
    server_msg               VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
    constraint_name          VARCHAR2(61);
  BEGIN
    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code in (40506, 40508, 40509, 40510) ) THEN

      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      IF ( CGTE$CHECK_CONSTRAINT_VIO(server_err, server_msg) ) THEN
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

      IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
        qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;

      IF (server_err = 2292) THEN
        IF (err_code = 40509) THEN
          qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
        END IF;
        QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.RAISE_FAILURE;
      END IF;
    END IF;

    IF (err_type = 'FRM' and
        err_code = 40735 ) THEN


      WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
        CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
      END LOOP;

      qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(server_err)||': '||server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
      qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;
    END IF;

    qms$forms_errors.push(err_type||'-'||to_char(err_code)||': '||ERROR_TEXT, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.raise_failure;

  END;
END;
     * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                      Yes
     * Execution Hierarchy                           Before
     * Display in 'Keyboard Help'                    Yes
     - 'Keyboard Help' Text                          
     - Trigger Steps                                 
     ----------
     * Name                                          KEY-HELP
     - Subclass Information                          
     - Comments                                      
     - Trigger Style                                 PL/SQL
     * Trigger Text

  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

   o Items

     * Comments                                      CG$IGNORE_ON_DESIGN_CAPTURE
     ^ Enabled                                       No

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;
       * Fire in Enter-Query Mode                    Yes

       ----------
       * Name                                        KEY-HELP
       - Subclass Information                        
       - Comments                                    
       - Trigger Style                               PL/SQL
       * Trigger Text                                

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGHP$CALL_HELP_FORM */
BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

BEGIN
  :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := '';
  IF (:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE IS NULL) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push(QMS$FORMS_ERRORS.MSGGETTEXT(23, 'Falta el fichero de ayuda o es incorrecto'), 'W', 'OFG', 23);
  ELSE
    :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE := :GLOBAL.CG$HP_HPATH || '';
    BEGIN
      CGHP$CALL_MS_HELP(0 ,:GLOBAL.CG$HP_HFILE);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
    END;
  END IF;
END;

Revision When       Who
         What
5.0      25-06-1998 S. Davelaar
         Headstart Template Package 5.0 BETA
5.0.1    18-08-1998 S. Davelaar
         - QMSSO$CONCEAL_ITEM added
         - CGSO$CANVAS_SPREAD now subclasses from CGSO$CANVAS_POPUP
         - QMSSO$MODAL_DOCUMENT_WINDOW added
         - parameter QMS$MENU_CALLING_FORM removed
         - triggers KEY-CLRFRM, PRE-FORM, QUERY_FIND, WHEN-NEW_BLOCK-INSTANCE,
           and WHEN-NEW-FORM-INSTANCE moved from object group QMS$STND_MODULE
           to object group QMS$MODULE
         - Lov QMS$ENABLED_LIST_LAMP changed to Record Group LOV
         - Record group QMS$ENABLE_LIST_LAMP added to object group QMS$MODULE
         - CG$LOV added (will be renamed to CGSO$LOV if OFG bug causing wrong
           LOV height to be generatedif CGSO$LOV is present, is fixed)
         - Background item VA's no longer inherit from qms$item_font (now using
           <Unspecified> setting)
         - Foreground prompt VA's no longer inherit from qms$prompt_font (now
           using <Unspecified> setting)
         - Visual attribute QMS$BOLD added
         - Visual attribute qms$gui_item_font added
         - item qms$block_info made non-navigable, and disabled
         - WHEN-WINDOW-CLOSED trigger added to QMSSO$MODULE
         - Iconic Calendar buttons now subclass QMSSO$CALENDAR_BUTTON,
           tooltips added
         - KEY-EXIT trigger added to QMSSO$MODULE
         - QMSSO$QUERY_ONLY_ITEM added
         - width and height of CGSO$WINDOW set to 1
         - Tooltip VA of QMSSO$TOOLBAR_BUTTON set to QMS$TOOLTIP
         - Fire in enter-query mode property switched on for
           WHEN-NEW-RECORD-INSTANCE trigger in QMSSO$MSEL_BLOCK (now required
           for highlighting queryable items)
         - QMSSO$NO_BEVEL_ITEM added
5.0.2    24-09-1998 S. Davelaar
         - Form level PRE-BLOCK trigger removed
         - PRE-BLOCK trigger added to CGSO$BLOCK
         - PRE-BLOCK trigger added to CGSO$BLOCK_CT
         - qms$block_info item made non-queryable, number of items displayed
           set to 1
         - QMSSO$WIZARD_BLOCK: Database Block property set to Yes
         - CONSOLE_WINDOW renamed to QMS$HIDDEN_ITEMS
         - QMSSO$TOOLBAR_WINDOW renamed to QMSSO$WEB_TOOLBAR_WINDOW
         - KEY-DOWN, KEY-UP, KEY-PRVREC, KEY-NXTREC, KEY-NXTREC added to
           QMSSO$MSEL_BLOCK
         - KEY-MENU added to QMSSO$MODULE
         - Query length set to 500 in CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM
         - WHEN-BUTTON-PRESSED trigger now owned by all QMSSO buttons individually,
           instead of inherited with the trigger text being overridden
         - Default value of parameter SWITCH_MENU set to DO_REPLACE
         - Renamed all icons in toolbar, calendar and CGSO$LOV_BUT to have qms prefix
         - KEY-EXIT trigger moved from object group QMSSO$MODULE to QMSSO$STND_MODULE
5.0.3    03-12-1998 S. Davelaar
         - Item CGSO$DATE: maximum length changed to 11
         - Added CGSO$DATETIME subclasses CGSO$DATE overriding datatype (set to
           datetime), and maximum length (set to 20)
         - Item QMSSO$TEXT: maximum length and query length set to 2000,
           Multi-line set to Yes
         - Item CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM: maximum length and query length set to 2000
5.0.3.1  14-01-1999 S. Davelaar
         - Parameter qmsolb50_revision renamed to objlib_revision, parameter
           objlib_name added and stored in object group QMSSO$MODULE
         - Object group QMSSO$MODULE: QMS$BLUE_FOREGROUND
         - Object group QMSSO$MODULE: Trigger KEY-HELP added
         - Object group QMSSO$MODULE: Paremeter SCHEMA_OWNER added
         - Block CGSO$BLOCK: POST-SELECT trigger added as work around for OFG
           bug 818001
         - Block CGSO$BLOCK_CT: Property query all records set to True
         - Block QMSSO$DYNAMIC_PROMPT_VALUE removed
         - Block QMSSO$WIZARD: item wizard_height added
         - Block QMSSO$WIZARD_SPLIT_BLOCK added, subclasses QMSSO$WIZARD, two
           own triggers added: ON-LOCK and WHEN-VALIDATE-RECORD
         - Visual Attribute QMS$BLUE_FOREGROUND added
         - Visual Attribute CALENDAR DISABLED: background color changed to gray
         - Visual Attribute QMS$PROMPT_LIGHT_BLUE renamed to QMS$PROMPT_LIGHTBLUE
         - Item QMSSO$TEXT: Trigger WHEN-NEW-ITEM-INSTANCE added
         - Item QMSSO$BLUE_TEXT added
         - Item QMSSO$BLUE_BOLD_TEXT: current record VA set to
           QMS$BLUE_FOREGROUND, subclasses from QMSSO$BLUE_TEXT
           trigger WHEN-TAB-PAGE-CHANGED removed
         - Item QMSSO$DISABLED_BUTTON added.
         - Tooltip property of item qms$block_info cleared in all blocks except
           QMSSO$BLOCK_MSEL
         - Items CALENDAR.OK and CALENDAR.CANCEL: Mouse navigate property set to True
         - Item CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM: when-mouse-click trigger removed
         - Item CGSO$DEFAULT_ITEM: Tooltip text set to 'No hint available.'
           (Work around for webforms bug, to be able to show tooltips on WEB)
         - All QMSSO$ buttons: calls to qms$event_item removed from WHEN-BUTTON-
           PRESSED triggers
         - New source item QMSSO$LOV_FORM_ITEM
         - Window QMSSO$DIALOG_WINDOW: Inherit menu property set to No
         - Window CALENDAR: Inherit menu property set to No
         - Popup Menu Item HELP_CONTEXT: PL/SQL code re-inherited from parent
         - Block QMS$TOOLBAR: WHEN-BUTTON-PRESSED changed into WHEN-MOUSE-CLICK
           trigger to be able to trap right-mouse-button click (forms bug 636000)
         - Block QMS$TOOLBAR: ORDER_BY poplist added with WHEN-LIST-CHANGED trigger.

     ^ Magic Item                                    Cut
     ^ Command Type                                  Null
     - Visible                                       Yes
     ^ Hint                                          Corta la selección actual y la pone en el apuntador
     ^ Help Description                              Removes the selected text and places it on the clipboard.  The contents of the clipboard can be pasted into text items or into other applications.  The contents of the clipboard are overwritten each time a Copy or Cut is performed.

The Copy and Cut commands are disabled when no text is selected.  The Cut command is also disabled if the current item is not updatable.

     * Name                                          LIST
     * Subclass Information                          
       ----------
       - Location                                    File
       - Source File                                 
       - Source Path                                 
       - Source Module                               
       - Source Owner                                
       - Source Level                                
       ----------
     - Comments                                      
     - Enabled                                       Yes
     ^ Label                                         Lista de &Valores...
     ^ Menu Item Type                                Plain
     ^ Magic Item                                    None
     ^ Command Type                                  PL/SQL
     - Menu Item Code                                

qms$menu.set_current_action('LIST');
execute_trigger('QMS$MENU_ITEM');
     - Visible                                       Yes
     ^ Hint                                          Invoca una ventana con una lista de valores valida desde la cual escoger
     ^ Help Description                              Displays a list of values (LOV) which is a scrollable pop-up window that provides you with a selection list containing one or more columns with all the valid values available for the current text item.  The LOV appears in a modal window which means you cannot work in other windows when an LOV is displayed.  You can move and resize the LOV (if the runtime window manager supports doing so).  The LOV window remains displayed until you select a single value or cancel the LOV.

Use the [Up] and [Down] keys or the scroll bar to navigate through the list.  Press the OK button or the [Accept] key to choose the selected value and close the list of values window.  Press the Cancel button to leave the list without making a selection.  When you select a value, the value is automatically returned into the current item.  Using an LOV can save keystrokes during data-entry and it ensures that the value entered is valid for that item.

There are LOV auto-reduction and search features to help you locate a value in a list.  To use auto-reduction, simply type the desired entry directly in the list pane of the LOV window.  As each character is entered, the list is reduced to only those values that match the string being entered.  Pressing [Delete Backwards] expands the reduced list of choices.  Auto-reduction works by comparing the string you entered with the values in the first column displayed in the LOV.  

You can use the search feature to locate a match for a specific text string and to do wildcard searches using "" and "_".  To use the search feature, enter your search criteria string in the LOV's Find field and press the Find button to execute the search.  The list is shortened to those choices whose first column values match your search criteria.  Note that if you precede the search criteria with a "" symbol, the search will be performed using all the LOV columns.

There is also an automatic search and complete feature that may have been implemented by the form designer.  An LOV evaluates a text item's current value as a search value.  That is, if you invoke the list of values in a text item and the item already contains a value, that value is automatically used as if you had entered it into the LOV's find field to reduce the list.  If the value would reduce the list to match only one record, the LOV does not display, but automatically enters the complete value into the current item.

For date or datetime fields, a calendar window is invoked which provides easy navigation between dates, months and years and allows you to quickly enter a date (and time for datetime fields).  Calendar windows help to ensure that you enter valid dates in the correct format.  The calendar window appears showing the same month as the current date in the date field with the date highlighted.  If no date exists in the date field, the calendar displays the current month with today's date highlighted.  Today's date is also underlined.  If there is a range of dates that is not valid for this field then the form designer can disable the dates on the calendar.

To help identify when an LOV is available for an item, a "<LIST>" (or "List of Values") lamp is displayed on the status line when you navigate into the item.

This function is also available through a button on the toolbar or directly adjacent the item.


For more information about runtime item interaction and examples, see the Oracle Forms Reference manual or the Getting Started with Forms manual.

     - Visible                                       Yes
     ^ Hint                                          Entra en modo de ayuda contextual
     ^ Help Description                              Switches the mouse pointer to a question mark "?", setting the application in help mode.  You can then click on any menu entry, button or item to get context-sensitive help.  A pop-up window will appear containing an explanation of the object.

This function is also available via the iconic help button on the toolbar.

/* CG$WHEN_NEW_FORM_INSTANCE */
PROCEDURE CG$WHEN_NEW_FORM_INSTANCE IS
BEGIN
/* CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS */
BEGIN
  CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS;
EXCEPTION
  WHEN OTHERS THEN
    CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
END;

/* CGSM$SHOW_STRIP_MENU */
BEGIN
  show_menu;
END;

/* CGLY$INIT_CANVASES */
BEGIN
  CGLY$CANVAS_MANAGEMENT;
END;


/* CGLT$INIT_TAB_BLOCKS                     */
/* Initialise tabbed canvases               */
BEGIN
   CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.ACTIVATE := TRUE;
   CGLT$TAB_BLOCKS.CGLT$NEW_BLOCK;
END;

/* CGBS$STARTUP */
BEGIN
  default_value('A', 'GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE');
  CGBS$.SET_RELATIONS( :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE );
  CGBS$SET_QUERY_MODE( :GLOBAL.CG$QUERY_MODE );
END;

/* CGNV$STARTUP_MODE */
DECLARE
wh_clause VARCHAR2(2000);
old_where VARCHAR2(2000);
BEGIN
  IF (:PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE != 'NORMAL') THEN
    wh_clause := '';
    IF :PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP IS NOT NULL THEN
      IF wh_clause IS NOT NULL THEN
        wh_clause := wh_clause || ' AND ';
      END IF;
      wh_clause := wh_clause ||
        'TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = :PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP';
    END IF;
    IF :PARAMETER.PDFECHA IS NOT NULL THEN
      IF wh_clause IS NOT NULL THEN
        wh_clause := wh_clause || ' AND ';
      END IF;
      wh_clause := wh_clause ||
        'FECHA = to_date(:PARAMETER.PDFECHA)';
    END IF;
    IF :PARAMETER.PNCLAVE IS NOT NULL THEN
      IF wh_clause IS NOT NULL THEN
        wh_clause := wh_clause || ' AND ';
      END IF;
      wh_clause := wh_clause ||
        'CLAVE = to_number(:PARAMETER.PNCLAVE)';
    END IF;

    old_where := get_block_property('CMP', DEFAULT_WHERE);

    CGNV$.INITIALISE_MODE(:SYSTEM.CURRENT_FORM, 'CMP', wh_clause, :PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE);

    IF( (:PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE = 'RESTRICTED NEW') OR
        (:PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE = 'RESTRICTED AUTO QUERY') OR
        (:PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE = 'RESTRICTED ENTER QUERY') ) THEN
      IF (:PARAMETER.PVTPOCMP IS NOT NULL) AND
         (get_item_property('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO',VISIBLE) = 'TRUE') THEN
        set_item_property('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO', QUERYABLE, PROPERTY_FALSE);
        set_item_property('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO', INSERT_ALLOWED, PROPERTY_FALSE);
        set_item_property('CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO', UPDATE_ALLOWED, PROPERTY_FALSE);
      END IF;
      IF (:PARAMETER.PDFECHA IS NOT NULL) AND
         (get_item_property('CMP.FECHA',VISIBLE) = 'TRUE') THEN
        set_item_property('CMP.FECHA', QUERYABLE, PROPERTY_FALSE);
        set_item_property('CMP.FECHA', INSERT_ALLOWED, PROPERTY_FALSE);
        set_item_property('CMP.FECHA', UPDATE_ALLOWED, PROPERTY_FALSE);
      END IF;
      IF (:PARAMETER.PNCLAVE IS NOT NULL) AND
         (get_item_property('CMP.CLAVE',VISIBLE) = 'TRUE') THEN
        set_item_property('CMP.CLAVE', QUERYABLE, PROPERTY_FALSE);
        set_item_property('CMP.CLAVE', INSERT_ALLOWED, PROPERTY_FALSE);
        set_item_property('CMP.CLAVE', UPDATE_ALLOWED, PROPERTY_FALSE);
      END IF;
    END IF;

    CGNV$.TIDYUP_MODE(:SYSTEM.CURRENT_FORM, 'CMP', old_where, :PARAMETER.CG$STARTUP_MODE);
  END IF;
END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   * Name                                            CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS

/* CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS */
PROCEDURE CGDV$POPULATE_DYNAMIC_LISTS IS
  temp NUMBER;  /* Return value of populate_group call */
  rg_id RECORDGROUP;  /* Return value of populate_group call */
BEGIN
  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''COMPROBANTES.ESTADO'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('CMP.ESTADO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_LOW_VALUE, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_ABBREVIATION, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_ABBREVIATION, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.MONEDAD', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_ABBREVIATION, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_ABBREVIATION, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.MONEDAH', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.MONEDA_LOCAL', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_LOW_VALUE, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''TIPO CUENTA CONTABILIDAD'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_LOW_VALUE, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('RTN.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''RETENCIONES.TIPO_RETENIDO'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('RTN.TIPO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_ABBREVIATION, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('RTN.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_MEANING, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''ESTADO MOVIMIENTOS'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('RTN.ESTADO', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

  rg_id := create_group_from_query('CGDV$DLRG',
    'select RV_LOW_VALUE, RV_LOW_VALUE '||
    'from   CG_REF_CODES '||
    'where  RV_DOMAIN = ''MONEDA'' '||
    'order by  2');
  temp := populate_group(rg_id);
  populate_list('OBLCNT.MONEDA', rg_id);
  delete_group(rg_id);

END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGFK$QRY_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGFK$QRY_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK(
   P_NOMBRE_REPORTE           IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_OBLIGACIONES             IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_RETENCIONES              IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA         IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_FORMULA_CLAVE            IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_NOMBRE                   IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOCMP_CODIGO            IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO     IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select VSTTPSCMP.NOMBRE
            ,VSTTPSCMP.FORMULA_CLAVE
            ,VSTTPSCMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
            ,VSTTPSCMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA
            ,VSTTPSCMP.RETENCIONES
            ,VSTTPSCMP.TPOCMP_OBLIGACIONES
            ,VSTTPSCMP.NOMBRE_REPORTE
      from   VISTA_TIPOS_COMPROBANTES VSTTPSCMP
      where  VSTTPSCMP.EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
      and    VSTTPSCMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMP_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_NOMBRE
          , P_FORMULA_CLAVE
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
          , P_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA
          , P_RETENCIONES
          , P_OBLIGACIONES
          , P_NOMBRE_REPORTE;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   - Subclass Information

/* CGFK$CHK_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$CHK_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_FK(
   P_NOMBRE_REPORTE           IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_OBLIGACIONES             IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_RETENCIONES              IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA         IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_FORMULA_CLAVE            IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_NOMBRE                   IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOCMP_CODIGO            IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO     IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select VSTTPSCMP.NOMBRE
            ,VSTTPSCMP.FORMULA_CLAVE
            ,VSTTPSCMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
            ,VSTTPSCMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA
            ,VSTTPSCMP.RETENCIONES
            ,VSTTPSCMP.TPOCMP_OBLIGACIONES
            ,VSTTPSCMP.NOMBRE_REPORTE
      from   VISTA_TIPOS_COMPROBANTES VSTTPSCMP
      where  VSTTPSCMP.EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
      and    VSTTPSCMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMP_CODIGO
      and    (VSTTPSCMP.EMP_CODIGO=:GLOBAL.CG$EMPRESA_CODIGO AND VSTTPSCMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD='D');
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_NOMBRE
          , P_FORMULA_CLAVE
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
          , P_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA
          , P_RETENCIONES
          , P_OBLIGACIONES
          , P_NOMBRE_REPORTE;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGSF$CLRLU_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_F */
PROCEDURE CGSF$CLRLU_CMP_CMP_VSTTPSCMP_F IS
BEGIN
  IF (:CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.TPOCMP_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.NOMBRE IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.NOMBRE := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.FORMULA_CLAVE := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.NOMBRE_SECUENCIA := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.RETENCIONES IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.RETENCIONES := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.OBLIGACIONES IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.OBLIGACIONES := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:CMP.NOMBRE_REPORTE IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :CMP.NOMBRE_REPORTE := NULL;
  END IF;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   - Subclass Information

/* CGFK$CHK_CMP_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$CHK_CMP_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_FK(
   P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPOCMP_CODIGO        IN VARCHAR2) IS
  CG$DUMMY VARCHAR2(1);
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select  '1'
      from   TIPOS_COMPROBANTES_EMPRESAS
      where  TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMP_CODIGO
      and    EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    CG$DUMMY;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGUV$CHK_CMP_PK
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGUV$CHK_CMP_PK */
PROCEDURE CGUV$CHK_CMP_PK(
   P_TPOCMP_CODIGO        IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_FECHA                IN DATE
  ,P_CLAVE                IN NUMBER
  ,P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_ROWID                IN VARCHAR2) IS
  CG$DUMMY VARCHAR2(1);
BEGIN
    DECLARE
      CURSOR C IS
        select  '1'
        from    COMPROBANTES
        where   TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
        and     CLAVE = P_CLAVE
        and     FECHA = P_FECHA
        and     TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMP_CODIGO
        and     ( P_rowid is null or
                  rowid <> P_rowid );
    BEGIN
      OPEN C;
      FETCH C
      into    CG$DUMMY;
      IF COTFOUND THEN
        CLOSE C;
        RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
      END IF;
      CLOSE C;
    END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGCD$SYNC_SRVR_CMP
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGCD$SYNC_SRVR_CMP */
PROCEDURE CGCD$SYNC_SRVR_CMP IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select CMP.MAYORIZADO
            ,CMP.TOTAL
      from   COMPROBANTES CMP
      where  CMP.rowid  = :CMP.rowid ;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into   :CMP.MAYORIZADO
          ,:CMP.TOTAL;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

/* CGFK$CHK_ASCCMP_ASCCMP_CMP_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$CHK_ASCCMP_ASCCMP_CMP_FK(

  ,P_CMP_CLAVE                IN NUMBER
  ,P_ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2 IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_CMP_FECHA                IN DATE    ) IS
  CG$DUMMY VARCHAR2(1);
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select  '1'
      from   COMPROBANTES
      where  FECHA = P_CMP_FECHA
      and    TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2
      and    CLAVE = P_CMP_CLAVE
      and    TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = P_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    CG$DUMMY;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

    into    CG$DUMMY;

  ,P_ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO2 IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_ASCTPOCMP_NOMBRE         IN VARCHAR2

        and     CMP_CLAVE = P_CMP_CLAVE

      into    CG$DUMMY;
      IF COTFOUND THEN
        CLOSE C;
        RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
      END IF;
      CLOSE C;

/* CGUI$GET_NEXT_MVM_SEQ */
PROCEDURE CGUI$GET_NEXT_MVM_SEQ(
   P_NEXT_VALUE IN OUT NUMBER) IS
BEGIN

    CURSOR C IS
      select  MVM_SEQ.NEXTVAL
      from    SYS.DUAL;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_NEXT_VALUE;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK(
   P_TIPO_DE_CUENTA               IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2           IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2    IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_CUENTA2                      IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO         IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_S_CODIGO                     IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO     IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_CODIGO                    IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_CODIGO                  IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_CODIGO                IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO             IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select SAXL3.NOMBRE
            ,SAXL3.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
            ,SAXL3.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO
            ,SAXL3.TIPO_DE_CUENTA
      from   SUBAUXILIARES_3 SAXL3
      where  SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.S_S_A_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.S_S_CODIGO = P_SS_S_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.S_CODIGO = P_SS_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.CODIGO = P_S_CODIGO
      and    SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_CUENTA2
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2
          , P_MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2
          , P_TIPO_DE_CUENTA;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK */
PROCEDURE CGSF$CLR_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK IS
BEGIN
  IF (:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_S_A_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.SS_S_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_S_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.SS_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.SS_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.S_CODIGO IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.S_CODIGO := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.CUENTA2 IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.CUENTA2 := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2 IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2 := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2 IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2 := NULL;
  END IF;
  IF (:MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA IS NOT NULL) THEN
    :MVM.TIPO_DE_CUENTA := NULL;
  END IF;
END;

/* CGFK$LKP_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$LKP_MVM_MVM_SAXL3_FK(
   P_FIELD_LEVEL                  IN     BOOLEAN
  ,P_TIPO_DE_CUENTA               IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2           IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2    IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_S_CODIGO                     IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_CODIGO                    IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_CODIGO                  IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_CODIGO                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO             IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO         IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO     IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO IN OUT VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.S_S_A_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.S_S_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.S_CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.CODIGO
            ,SAXL3.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
            ,SAXL3.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO
            ,SAXL3.TIPO_DE_CUENTA
      from   SUBAUXILIARES_3 SAXL3
      where  SAXL3.NOMBRE = :MVM.CUENTA2
      and    (SAXL3.S_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO=:GLOBAL.CG$EMPRESA_CODIGO AND SAXL3.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD='D');
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO
          , P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
          , P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
          , P_SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO
          , P_SS_S_A_CODIGO
          , P_SS_S_CODIGO
          , P_SS_CODIGO
          , P_S_CODIGO
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD2
          , P_MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO2
          , P_TIPO_DE_CUENTA;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_MVM_MVM_PLNCNT_FK(
   P_TIPO_DE_CUENTA_PLN           IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1      IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO            IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD     IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_NOMBRE                       IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_CODIGO_PLAN                  IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_S_CODIGO                     IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_CODIGO                    IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_CODIGO                  IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_CODIGO                IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO             IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO         IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO     IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.CODIGO
            ,PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.NOMBRE
            ,PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
            ,PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO
            ,PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.ASOCIACION
            ,PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.TIPO_DE_CUENTA
      from   PLAN_DE_CUENTAS PLAN_DE_CUENTAS
      where  PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.EMP_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_EMP_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.MYR_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_MYR_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.CNT_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CNT_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.SCNT_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_SC_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.AXL_CODIGO = P_SS_S_A_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.SAXL_CODIGO = P_SS_S_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.SAXL2_CODIGO = P_SS_CODIGO
      and    PLAN_DE_CUENTAS.SAXL3_CODIGO = P_S_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_CODIGO_PLAN
          , P_NOMBRE
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
          , P_MONEDA_DE_TRABAJO
          , P_ASOCIACION_MOVIMIENTOS1
          , P_TIPO_DE_CUENTA_PLN;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

/* CGFK$CHK_MVM_MVM_OBL_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$CHK_MVM_MVM_OBL_FK(
   P_OBL_OBL_ID IN NUMBER) IS
  CG$DUMMY VARCHAR2(1);
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select  '1'
      from   OBLIGACIONES
      where  OBL_ID = P_OBL_OBL_ID;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    CG$DUMMY;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGFK$CHK_MVM_MVM_CMP_FK
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGFK$CHK_MVM_MVM_CMP_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$CHK_MVM_MVM_CMP_FK(
   P_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO    IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_CMP_FECHA                   IN DATE
  ,P_CMP_CLAVE                   IN NUMBER  ) IS
  CG$DUMMY VARCHAR2(1);
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select  '1'
      from   COMPROBANTES
      where  CLAVE = P_CMP_CLAVE
      and    FECHA = P_CMP_FECHA
      and    TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = P_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
      and    TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_CMP_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    CG$DUMMY;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

/* CGCD$SYNC_SRVR_MVM */
PROCEDURE CGCD$SYNC_SRVR_MVM IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select MVM.OBL_OBL_ID
      from   MOVIMIENTOS MVM
      where  MVM.rowid  = :MVM.rowid ;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into   :MVM.OBL_OBL_ID;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_VSTTPSRTN_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_VSTTPSRTN_FK(
   P_VSTTPSRTN_TPORTN_VALOR     IN OUT NUMBER
  ,P_TPORTNEMP_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_DESCRIPCION                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD   IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_FORMULA_IVA                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_FORMULA_RETENCION          IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_EMP_CODIGO                 IN     VARCHAR2
  ,P_TPORTN_CODIGO              IN     NUMBER  ) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select VSTTPSRTN.FORMULA_RETENCION
            ,VSTTPSRTN.FORMULA_IVA
            ,VSTTPSRTN.ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
            ,VSTTPSRTN.DESCRIPCION
            ,VSTTPSRTN.TPORTNEMP_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA
            ,VSTTPSRTN.TPORTN_VALOR
      from   VISTA_TIPOS_RETENCIONES VSTTPSRTN
      where  VSTTPSRTN.TPORTN_CODIGO = P_TPORTN_CODIGO
      and    VSTTPSRTN.EMP_CODIGO = P_EMP_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_FORMULA_RETENCION
          , P_FORMULA_IVA
          , P_ESTADO_DE_DISPONIBILIDAD
          , P_DESCRIPCION
          , P_TPORTNEMP_NOMBRE_SECUENCIA
          , P_VSTTPSRTN_TPORTN_VALOR;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;

/* CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_PRD_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_PRD_FK(

    IF COTFOUND THEN

   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_EMP_FK */
PROCEDURE CGFK$QRY_RTN_RTN_EMP_FK(
   P_L_PRV_PROVINCIA          IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_CNT_CANTON             IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_PRQ_PARROQUIA          IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_PRQ_CODIGO         IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_PRQ_CNT_CODIGO     IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_PRQ_CNT_PRV_CODIGO IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_DIRECCION          IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_RUC                IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_TELEFONO           IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_L_EMP_DESCRIPCION        IN OUT VARCHAR2
  ,P_EMP_CODIGO               IN     VARCHAR2) IS
BEGIN
  DECLARE
    CURSOR C IS
      select L_EMP.DESCRIPCION
            ,L_EMP.TELEFONO
            ,L_EMP.RUC
            ,L_EMP.DIRECCION
            ,L_EMP.PRQ_CNT_PRV_CODIGO
            ,L_EMP.PRQ_CNT_CODIGO
            ,L_EMP.PRQ_CODIGO
            ,L_PRQ.PARROQUIA
            ,L_CNT.CANTON
            ,L_PRV.PROVINCIA
      from   EMPRESAS L_EMP
            ,PARROQUIAS L_PRQ
            ,CANTONES L_CNT
            ,PROVINCIAS L_PRV
      where  L_EMP.CODIGO = P_EMP_CODIGO
      and    L_PRQ.CNT_CODIGO = L_EMP.PRQ_CNT_CODIGO
      and    L_PRQ.CNT_PRV_CODIGO = L_EMP.PRQ_CNT_PRV_CODIGO
      and    L_PRQ.CODIGO = L_EMP.PRQ_CODIGO
      and    L_CNT.CODIGO = L_PRQ.CNT_CODIGO
      and    L_CNT.PRV_CODIGO = L_PRQ.CNT_PRV_CODIGO
      and    L_PRV.CODIGO = L_CNT.PRV_CODIGO;
  BEGIN
    OPEN C;
    FETCH C
    into    P_L_EMP_DESCRIPCION
          , P_L_EMP_TELEFONO
          , P_L_EMP_RUC
          , P_L_EMP_DIRECCION
          , P_L_EMP_PRQ_CNT_PRV_CODIGO
          , P_L_EMP_PRQ_CNT_CODIGO
          , P_L_EMP_PRQ_CODIGO
          , P_L_PRQ_PARROQUIA
          , P_L_CNT_CANTON
          , P_L_PRV_PROVINCIA;
    IF COTFOUND THEN
      CLOSE C;
      RAISE NO_DATA_FOUND;
    END IF;
    CLOSE C;
  END;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGRI$SERVER_VIO_CMP
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGRI$SERVER_VIO_CMP */
PROCEDURE CGRI$SERVER_VIO_CMP(
   P_SQLCODE   IN NUMBER
  ,P_OPERATION IN VARCHAR2) IS
  server_err       NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
  server_msg       VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;
  sql_error        NUMBER         := abs(P_SQLCODE);
  constraint_name  VARCHAR2(61);
BEGIN
  IF ( not (sql_error in  (1, 2290, 2291, 2292) OR (sql_error >= 20000 AND sql_error <= 20999) ) ) THEN
    CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END IF;
  WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
    CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
  END LOOP;

  IF (server_err >= 20000 AND server_err <= 20999) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push('' || nls_initcap(P_OPERATION) || ' en Comprobantes ha provocado la siguiente violación:', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.push(''||CGTE$STRIP_FIRST_ERROR(server_msg), 'E', 'OFG', 0);
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  constraint_name := CGTE$STRIP_CONSTRAINT(server_msg);

  IF (server_err = 1) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push('' || nls_initcap(P_OPERATION) || ' en Comprobantes ha provocado la siguiente violación:', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
  IF (server_err = 2290) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push('' || nls_initcap(P_OPERATION) || ' en Comprobantes ha provocado la siguiente violación:', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;

  IF (server_err = 2291) THEN
    qms$forms_errors.push('' || nls_initcap(P_OPERATION) || ' en Comprobantes ha provocado la siguiente violación:', 'E', 'OFG', 0);
    qms$forms_errors.push(server_msg, 'I', 'OFG', 0);
    RAISE FORM_TRIGGER_FAILURE;
  END IF;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGRI$CU_CMP
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGRI$CU_CMP */
PROCEDURE CGRI$CU_CMP(
   P_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO IN VARCHAR2
  ,P_FECHA                   IN DATE
  ,P_CLAVE                   IN NUMBER
  ,P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO    IN VARCHAR2) IS
  CG$DUMMY VARCHAR2(1);  /* Dummy variable */
  values_changed BOOLEAN;  /* Flag to show primary key values changed */
BEGIN
  BEGIN
    select  '1'
    into    CG$DUMMY
    from    COMPROBANTES
    where   COMPROBANTES.CLAVE = P_CLAVE
    or  COMPROBANTES.FECHA = P_FECHA
    and     (   COMPROBANTES.CLAVE <> P_CLAVE
         or  COMPROBANTES.FECHA <> P_FECHA );
    values_changed := TRUE;
  EXCEPTION
    WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
      values_changed := FALSE;

  END;
  IF (values_changed) THEN
    BEGIN
      update  RETENCIONES
      set     CMP_FECHA = :CMP.FECHA
            , CMP_CLAVE = :CMP.CLAVE
      where   (CMP_FECHA, TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO, TPORTNEMP_EMP_CODIGO, CMP_CLAVE) =
              (select  CMP.FECHA, CMP.TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO, CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO, CMP.CLAVE
               from    COMPROBANTES CMP
               where   CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
               and     CMP.CLAVE = P_CLAVE
               and     CMP.FECHA = P_FECHA
               and     CMP.TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGRI$SERVER_VIO_CMP(SQLCODE, 'UPDATE');
    END;

    BEGIN
      update  ASOCIACIONES_COMPROBANTE
      set     CMP_FECHA = :CMP.FECHA
            , CMP_CLAVE = :CMP.CLAVE
      where   (CMP_FECHA, ASCTPOCMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO, CMP_CLAVE, CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO) =
              (select  CMP.FECHA, CMP.TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO, CMP.CLAVE, CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
               from    COMPROBANTES CMP
               where   CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
               and     CMP.CLAVE = P_CLAVE
               and     CMP.FECHA = P_FECHA
               and     CMP.TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGRI$SERVER_VIO_CMP(SQLCODE, 'UPDATE');
    END;

    BEGIN
      update  MOVIMIENTOS
      set     CMP_CLAVE = :CMP.CLAVE
            , CMP_FECHA = :CMP.FECHA
      where   (CMP_CLAVE, CMP_FECHA, CMP_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO, CMP_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO) =
              (select  CMP.CLAVE, CMP.FECHA, CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO, CMP.TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO
               from    COMPROBANTES CMP
               where   CMP.TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_EMP_CODIGO
               and     CMP.CLAVE = P_CLAVE
               and     CMP.FECHA = P_FECHA
               and     CMP.TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO = P_TPOCMPEMP_TPOCMP_CODIGO);
    EXCEPTION
      WHEN OTHERS THEN
        CGRI$SERVER_VIO_CMP(SQLCODE, 'UPDATE');
    END;
  END IF;
END;
   - Program Unit Type                               Message 8393 not found;  product=forms50; facility=FMD

   ----------
   * Name                                            CGRI$SERVER_VIO_MVM
   - Subclass Information                            
   - Comments                                        
   * Program Unit Text                               

/* CGRI$SERVER_VIO_MVM */
PROCEDURE CGRI$SERVER_VIO_MVM(
   P_SQLCODE   IN NUMBER
  ,P_OPERATION IN VARCHAR2) IS
  server_err       NUMBER         := abs(DBMS_ERROR_CODE);
  server_msg       VARCHAR2(2000) := DBMS_ERROR_TEXT;

  constraint_name  VARCHAR2(61);
BEGIN
  IF ( not (sql_error in  (1, 2290, 2291, 2292) OR (sql_error >= 20000 AND sql_error <= 20999) ) ) THEN
    CGTE$OTHER_EXCEPTIONS;
  END IF;
  WHILE (server_err = 604) LOOP
    CGTE$POP_ERROR_STACK(server_err, server_msg);
  END LOOP;

  IF (server_err >= 20000 AND server_err <= 20999) THEN

   ----------

   - Subclass Information

/* CGRI$DEL_MOVIMIENTOS */
PROCEDURE CGRI$DEL_MOVIMIENTOS(
   P_MVM_ID IN NUMBER) IS
BEGIN
  BEGIN
  delete from  SALDOS
  where  MVM_MVM_ID = P_MVM_ID;
  EXCEPTION
  WHEN OTHERS THEN
    CGRI$SERVER_VIO_MVM(SQLCODE, 'DELETE');
  END;
